  arrows-0.2.1.ebuild:
  Fixes for compatability with cabal-1.2 and ghc-6.8.

  12 Dec 2007; Ferris McCormick <fmccor@gentoo.org> arrows-0.2.1.ebuild:
  Sparc stable --- part of Bug #201984.

